title: Internal Revenue Cumulative Bulletin
additional-note: This is a compilation of material from the Internal Revenue Bulletin, a US government publication.  It was published by the IRS until 2008.  In 2015, Berman Press registered copyright claims to 2009 volumes, apparently published under an arrangement with the IRS.  We do not know the basis for those copyright claims, and cannot judge their validity.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Nat Bender for copyright research on this title.
